Class EarthquakeMarker

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.fhpotsdam.unfolding.marker.AbstractMarker
      • de.fhpotsdam.unfolding.marker.SimplePointMarker
        • EarthquakeMarker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    de.fhpotsdam.unfolding.marker.Marker

    public class EarthquakeMarker
extends de.fhpotsdam.unfolding.marker.SimplePointMarker
    EarthquakeMarker is a class for the customized representation of earthquakes in an unfolding map. It inherits from the basic marker class SimplePointMarker of the unfolding package.
    Version:
    1.2
    Author:
    Merlin Unterfinger
